Output assets/demo.gif

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1400
Set Height 800
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Hide
Type "alias stack='node dist/cli.js'" Enter
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Type "stack --tool codex"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3.5s

Type "stack --kind skill --search wiki"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3.5s

Type "stack --versions-only"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "stack --doctor"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s
